column9: Ekspor Indonesia periode Januari hingga Oktober 2020 lalu memang menggembirakan, yakni mengalami surplus sebesar US$17,07 miliar. Namun, jangan cepat berpuas diri. Potensi ekspor Indonesia masih jauh lebih besar dari nilai tersebut.

column3: When life tries to push you down, step on you, take your health, squash your dreams, you have to get back up again. Outlast whatâ€™s trying to defeat you. The power in you is greater than any power thatâ€™s trying to stop you.
column4: God is about to take you higher. Things that have held you back are being broken. New doors are about to open, giants are about to be defeated, talent is about to come out of you that you didnâ€™t know you had.
column5: You may have difficulties now, in your health, your finances, your marriage. You could live worried and panicked. But when you know youâ€™re in a safe place, where God has you hidden, then you can live in peace.

column7:
When you honor God, when you stay close to Him, you have an advantage. He hides you when trouble comes. He makes you invisible to the enemy.

Click here to watch, "Invisible to the Enemy": https://t.co/kMfAhXGqHJ https://t.co/DMYDJoz7Af
column8: Enemies may be knocking at your door: debt, trouble, sickness, calamity. Stay in peace; youâ€™re invisible to the enemy. It may show up, but itâ€™s not going to find you.
column9: Faith and fear have something in common. They both ask us to believe something that we canâ€™t see. Whichever one you get in agreement with is the one thatâ€™s going to come to pass.
column10: That difficulty is not how your story ends; God has the final say. Heâ€™s not only going to take care of whatâ€™s trying to stop you, but Heâ€™s going to bring you out better.
column11: Trouble is not going to come near you. Why? Youâ€™re in the shelter of the Most High. He has you covered. Heâ€™s covered your health, covered your marriage, covered your children, covered your finances, covered your dreams.
column12: God can make you invisible to the enemy. Plans that were sent to stop you, strategies designed to keep you from your destiny, cannot stand against our God.
column13: God is your vindicator. He sees whatâ€™s happening. If youâ€™ll stay on the high road, Heâ€™ll make it up to you.
column14: If youâ€™ll get rid of the bitterness, the offense, the critical spirit, the negativity, youâ€™ll get your passion back; youâ€™ll get that spring in your step. Youâ€™ll not only enjoy life more, but youâ€™ll see Godâ€™s favor and blessings in new ways.
column15: You have to trust the process. While youâ€™re waiting, things are growing; things are developing. God is bringing it all together.
column16:
God called you an eagle; He created you to soar. Donâ€™t let a sour attitude keep you grounded. Itâ€™s time to rise to new levels, to soar to new heights.

Check out "A Fresh New Attitude" on Podcast here! https://t.co/KpspxxmnN3
